data.description: For families seeking new homes situated in a rural setting while perfectly located between Winter Haven and Bartow shopping and dining, the community of Liberty Ridge is for you. This solar community is ideal for home owners looking to for a welcoming community at an affordable price. Liberty Ridge includes professionally landscaped common grounds and an open area to enjoy outside.With homes starting at just $199,990, Liberty Ridge is a cost-effective solar community with Lennar's Everything's Included® promise. Each home comes with stainless steal appliances, blinds, and more.This Patriotic community features a monument that honors those that have served our country. Veterans looking to purchase a home at Liberty Ridge are eligible for special perks to show our appreciation. Homeowners looking to live in a quiet city but still in close proximity to major areas such as Winter Haven, Orlando, and Tampa will love living at Liberty Ridge.
